### -------------------------
### AUTH & USERS
### -------------------------

### 1. Register a new patient
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Melly",
  "password": "TestPass123",
  "email": "melly1@example.com",
  "role": "Patient"
}

### 2. Login as Patient
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Melly",
  "password": "TestPass123"
}

> {% client.global.set("patient_token", response.body.access) %}

### 3. Login as Admin
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "AdminPass123"
}

> {% client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.access) %}

### 4. Login as Doctor
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/users/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "doctor1",
  "password": "DoctorPass123"
}

> {% client.global.set("doctor_token", response.body.access) %}

---

### -------------------------
### PATIENT PROFILES
### -------------------------

### 5. Patient creates profile
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/patients/
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date_of_birth": "1990-05-10",
  "address": "Nairobi",
  "phone_number": "0712345678"
}

### 6. Admin views all patient profiles
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/patients/
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

---

### -------------------------
### APPOINTMENTS
### -------------------------

### 7. Patient creates an appointment
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/appointments/
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctor": 1,
  "date": "2025-09-05",
  "time": "10:00:00",
  "reason": "Regular check-up"
}

### 8. Doctor views all appointments
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/appointments/
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}

---

### -------------------------
### QUEUE
### -------------------------

### 9. Admin/Nurse adds appointment to queue
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/queue/
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointment": 1,
  "position": 1,
  "status": "waiting"
}

### 10. View queue
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/queue/
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

---

### -------------------------
### MEDICAL RECORDS
### -------------------------

### 11. Doctor creates a medical record
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/records/
Authorization: Bearer {{doctor_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patient": 1,
  "diagnosis": "Flu",
  "treatment": "Rest and hydration",
  "notes": "Patient recovering well"
}

### 12. Patient views their own medical records
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/records/
Authorization: Bearer {{patient_token}}

